metadata.description: From the atelier of Paloceras comes a surrealist dream made tangible in these limited-edition spectacles.They invite one to embrace the fantastical, where beauty and innovation merge in a surreal symphony of the senses, and the wearer becomes an otherworldly being, suspended in time and space.
